# Data Cleaning & Preparation

## Objective
Clean and prepare a raw e-commerce dataset by handling missing values, verifying duplicate records, standardizing data formats, and validating data consistency.

## Dataset Information
- Records: 1200
- Columns: 14

## Tasks Performed
- Identified missing values
- Replaced missing CouponCode values with "No Coupon"
- Checked duplicate rows
- Verified unique Order IDs
- Standardized date format (YYYY-MM-DD)
- Cleaned text fields
- Validated TotalPrice calculations
- Exported cleaned dataset

## Tools Used
- Python
- Pandas
- NumPy
- Jupyter Notebook

## Results
- Missing Values: 0
- Duplicate Rows: 0
- Duplicate Order IDs: 0
- Standardized Date Format: Yes
- Data Validation Passed: Yes
